      "authorUrl": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/113559833571360977516?hl=id",
      "rating": 5,
      "text": "The best coffee taste in town if you really a coffee lover, you should try them. Especially the coffee flavor's are the best; rum, hazelnut, kalua are boosting the body and mind. The coffee booth is so manly...it is supporting the cafe atmosphere while you sitting enjoying your favorite a coffee drink.",
      "textTranslated": "Jika Anda benar-benar pencinta kopi, Anda harus mencobanya. Terutama rasa kopinya yang terbaik; rum, hazelnut, dan kalua sangat menyegarkan tubuh dan pikiran. Kedai kopinya sangat maskulin...mendukung suasana kafe saat Anda duduk menikmati minuman kopi favorit Anda.",
